A-links

A-links offers a wide range of tools and resources to help businesses. A smart SEO and link-building strategy is at the core of the A-links. They use clever methods to boost Google’s ranking. The product blends expertise with flexibility, helping brands to succeed in the ever-changing SEO world

About

Brand: A-links

Location: Malta

Industry: Marketing

Budget:: $10,000 – $49,000

Clutch Review: 

5.0
 5/5

Product link: a-links.com

Type of software: Web App

Scope of work: Back-end, Front-end, UI/UX, Quality Assurance

We started from the initial requirements needed, the discovery stage of reviewing and analyzing the pros and cons of the competitors. After that, we have been working with the prototyping, designing, development, QA stage, and preparation for the release.

Technologies

PHP 8.2

Laravel

PostgreSQL

JavaScript

Vue

Docker

DigitalOcean

Stripe

What our client
wanted

Andreas Dahlqvist

Founder and CEO

We needed to create a platform to combine marketing expertise with adaptability, empowering brands to thrive in the dynamic world of SEO

Challenge

  • There was a challenge to make an accurate filtration here. Working through the niche filtration was tricky from the design part and FE development. We had to find a user-friendly solution on the design part and make it both flexible and reliable from the technical point of view.

Key features

  • Links builder - it is a feature in building a strategy to generate more backlinks for a company's website
  • Niche filtration - it is the feature, that helps you to identify the right field of the business activity for the future promotion
  • Ahrefs analysis - is a powerhouse capable of pretty much any backlink research task

Project Team

Artem

Team Lead​

Anastasiia

Project Manager

Ihor

QA

BE developer

Dmytro

FE developer

Designer

Designer

Get a quote

Client’s review

Andreas Dahlqvist

Founder and CEO

The team was professional, responsive, and truly committed to the success of the project. They went above and beyond to ensure that everything was done to the highest standard, and their attention to detail was outstanding. I am thrilled with the final product, and I would highly recommend QT Global

5.0
 5/5

Business Value

We have created a web app that automates the process of SEO marketing services;

Fully tested and deployed system;

The app is already attracting users and bringing profit to the company

Let's start. It's easier than you think.

Contact us
